410
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:36,960
We didn't know he knew Angry Lions.
He attacked us by surprise.

411
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:41,350
You don't have enough Qi and you snuck off?

412
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:45,900
Go away. Kill all those merchant fleet people.

413
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:49,640
Don't let others say we don't keep our promises.

414
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:51,690
Yes.

415
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,650
