420
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:26,200
Those merchants are not Fight Practitioners.

421
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:30,390
You bully the weak.
How can you call yourself a decent clan?

422
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,500
