425
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:43,800
Good. Yan Xiao, right?

426
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:49,790
I don't need to kill ants myself.

427
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:55,300
If you can take three attacks from me,

428
00:40:56,090 --> 00:40:58,820
I will pardon you today.

429
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,450
Yes.

