00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,790
Three attacks.

431
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,800
Three attacks.

432
00:41:21,600 --> 00:41:24,030
Angry Lions!

433
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:45,750
Yan Xiao isn't dead.
I will take another attack.

